law.history: Repealed 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 198. -- Amended 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 152, sec. 98. -- Amended 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 151, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1565b-11.
